crosoft YaHei&quot;; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 1px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"></span></strong></span></section></section></section></section><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"/></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\">1.</strong><strong style=\"caret-color: red; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">什么是八类网</strong><strong style=\"caret-color: red; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">线</strong><strong style=\"caret-color: red; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"></strong></span></p><p><br/></p><p><section data-role=\"paragraph\" class=\"\" style=\"white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><br/></p></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\" class=\"\" style=\"white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><p style=\"margin-top: 0.63em; margin-bottom: 1.8em; text-align: justify; padding: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; border-width: 0px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; color: rgb(25, 25, 25); letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.75em; font-family: Arial, 微软雅黑, 宋体, simsun, sans-serif; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\">八类网线（Cat8）是<span style=\"font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: red; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\">最新一代双屏蔽（SFTP）网线，<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-indent: 32px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\">可支持2000MHz的带宽，且传输速率高达40Gb/s，但传输距离在30米以内才能达到其<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 1.5px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\">最佳<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 1.5px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\">性能</span></span>，因此常用于短距离数据中心的服务器、交换机、配线架以及其他设备的连接。</span></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0.63em; margin-bottom: 1.8em; text-align: center; padding: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; border-width: 0px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; color: rgb(25, 25, 25); letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.75em; font-family: Arial, 微软雅黑, 宋体, simsun, sans-serif; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/ueditor/php/upload/image/20210730/1627610858932474.jpg\" title=\"1627610858932474.jpg\" alt=\"O1CN014iSDG61n0PiG3jx5R_!!398685027.jpg\"/></p><section data-role=\"paragraph\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><br/></p></section></section></p><p><br/></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\">2.</strong><strong style=\"caret-color: red; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">八类网线标准</strong><strong style=\"caret-color: red; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"></strong></span></p><p><br/></p><p><section data-role=\"paragraph\" class=\"\" style=\"white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><br/></p><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.5em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); letter-spacing: 1px; font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\">Cat8 八类网线的相关标准由美国通信工业协会(TIA )TR-43委员会于2016年正式发布，具体如下：</span></section></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\" style=\"white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; padding: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.75em; font-family: Helvetica, Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\">1．符合IEEE 802.3bq 25G / 40GBASE-T标准，规定了Cat8八类网线的最小传输速率，可支持25 Gbps和40 Gbps的网络布线。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; padding: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.75em; font-family: Helvetica, Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\">2．符合ANSI / TIA-568-C.2-1标准，规定了Cat8八类网线的通道和永久链路，并包含电阻不平衡、TCL和ELTCTL的限制。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; padding: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.75em; font-family: Helvetica, Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\">3．符合ANSI / TIA-1152-A标准，规定了Cat8八类网线现场测试仪测量和精度要求。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; padding: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.75em; font-family: Helvetica, Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\">4．符合ISO / IEC-11801标准，规定了I/II 类Cat8八类网线的通道和永久链路。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; padding: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.75em; font-family: Helvetica, Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><br/></p></section></p><p><br/></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\">3.</strong><strong style=\"caret-color: red; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">八类网线与其他网线参数对比图</strong><strong style=\"caret-color: red; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"></strong></span></p><p><br/></p><p><section data-role=\"paragraph\" class=\"\" style=\"white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><br/></p></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\" class=\"\" style=\"white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-indent: 32px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\">八类线和其他类型网线的区别是比较大的，主要体现在</span><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-indent: 32px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\">传输速率、频率带宽、传输距离</strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-indent: 32px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\">等方面。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><br/></p></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\" class=\"\" style=\"white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: justify; padding: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.75em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-align: left; text-indent: 32px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\">虽然八类网线和七/超七类网线都属于屏蔽型双绞线，能应用于<span style=\"font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 1.5px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\">高速宽带环境，例如数据中心和带宽密集的地方。</span>虽然八类网线在使用过程中想要达到<span style=\"font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 1.5px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\">最优性能仅限于</span>30m以内，<span style=\"font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 1.5px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\">但传输速率、频率<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 1.5px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\">带</span>宽远超于其他网线。</span></span></p></section></p><p><br/></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; outline: none 0px !important;\"><br/></strong><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; outline: none 0px !important;\"></strong></span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; outline: none 0px !important;\">4</strong><strong style=\"caret-color: red; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">.八类网线的优势</strong><strong style=\"caret-color: red; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"></strong></span></p><p><br/></p><p><section class=\"\" style=\"white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; outline: none 0px !important;\"><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; outline: none 0px !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; outline: none 0px !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); letter-spacing: 1.5px; font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); letter-spacing: 1.5px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\">八类网线</span>可以共享RJ45端口，这也就意味着它可以轻松的将网络速率从1G升级至10G、25G和40G；除此之外，<span style=\"font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); letter-spacing: 1.5px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\">八类网线</span>也是即插即用的，也能像其它类别的网线现场端接，非常易于部署。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; padding: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; outline: none 0px !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 1.5px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\">同时，由于网线的成本较低，双绞线一直是以太网中最具成本效益的解决方案，<span style=\"font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); letter-spacing: 1.5px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\">八类网线</span>也不例外。根据市场反馈，在部署25G/40GBASE-T网络时，<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 1.5px; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\">在传输距离小于30米时，八类网线比光纤跳线更具成本效益，</span>所以仍然热衷使用八类网线</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; outline: none 0px !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 1.5px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; outline: none 0px !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: b