stify;\">获评南山区<strong style=\"text-align: center; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify;\">2021-2023年度</span></strong>“绿色通道”企业</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify;\">荣誉称号，<span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); letter-spacing: 1px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"></span></span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); letter-spacing: 1px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">为公司带来了一系列辖区内的优惠政策以及便捷服务。</span></span></span></p></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><p style=\"text-align:left;max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><br/></p><section data-role=\"paragraph\" class=\"\"><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent: 0em;letter-spacing: 1.5px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px; text-align: left; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 16px;\">据悉，南山区从1998年起，在全区范围内开展评选“绿色通道”企业活动，并对获选企业颁发“绿色通行证”，使持证企业享受到更优惠的政策和更便捷的服务。“绿色通道”评定企业范围覆盖南山区纳税百强、工业百强、上市企业、独角兽企业等。</span></p><section data-role=\"paragraph\" class=\"\"><p><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20210812/1628761441621165.png\" title=\"1628761441621165.png\" alt=\"2.png\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20210812/1628761495753413.png\" title=\"1628761495753413.png\" alt=\"640.png\"/></p></section><p style=\"text-align: center; text-indent: 0em; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px; caret-color: red; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"caret-color: red; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(241, 92, 25); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">”绿色通道“企业可享受服务政策（截取部分）</span><span style=\"caret-color: red; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(241, 92, 25); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent: 0em;letter-spacing: 1.5px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px; caret-color: red; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 16px;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent: 0em;letter-spacing: 1.5px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px; caret-color: red; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 14px; caret-color: red; letter-spacing: 0.544px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">此荣誉的获得，<span style=\"font-size: 14px; caret-color: red; color: rgb(54, 54, 54); letter-spacing: 0.544px; font-family: PingFangSC-Light, sans-serif;\">代表南山区政府对公司价值和贡献的支持与认可，</span></span>意味着公司可享受南山区包括人才扶持措施、纳税服务、知识产权保护、人才健康管理等111条服务措施，在出入境、户政、申报认定等涉及政府审批事项上，可享受“直通车”式的便利审批与跟踪协助，<span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; caret-color: red; color: rgb(54, 54, 54); letter-spacing: 0.544px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">为企业提供精准式服务。</span></span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent: 0em;letter-spacing: 1.5px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><br/></p></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\" class=\"\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20210812/1628761515794662.jpg\" title=\"1628761515794662.jpg\" alt=\"3.jpg\"/></p></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\" class=\"\"><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent: 0em;letter-spacing: 1.5px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"caret-color: red; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 16px;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent: 0em;letter-spacing: 1.5px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"caret-color: red; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 16px;\">未来，<span style=\"caret-color: red; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; letter-spacing: 0.5px; text-align: left; white-space: pre-wrap;\">在政府部门的保驾护航下，</span>在政策利好、行业向上的大环境下，秋叶原将继续保持<span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63); caret-color: red; letter-spacing: 0.544px; font-family: PingFangSC-Light, sans-serif;\">行业领先的创效能力，<span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; caret-color: red; letter-spacing: 0.544px;\">在全球科技革命和产业变革中稳步高质量发展，继续发挥优秀企业的示范带动作用。</span></span></span></p><p style=\"caret-color: red;letter-spacing: 0.544px;\"><br/></p></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\" class=\"\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20210812/1628761527675606.jpg\" title=\"1628761527675606.jpg\" alt=\"4.jpg\"/></p></section><section style=\"margin-right: 0%; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0%; box-sizing: border-box; height: 0px; overflow: hidden;\"></section></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\" class=\"\"><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 16px;\"><strong><span style=\"caret-color: red; font-size: 13px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><br/></span></strong></span></p><p><font color=\"#3f3f3f\" face=\"Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\"><span style=\"caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 16px;\"><b>关于公司：</b></span></font></p><p><strong><span style=\"caret-color: red; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">深圳市前海秋叶原新材料科技有限公司</span></strong><span style=\"caret-color: red; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">成立于2015年9月，是</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center; caret-color: red; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">广东前海秋叶原集团</span><span style=\"caret-color: red; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">的全资子公司之一。主营业务大宗商品有色金属铜杆，电解铜，铝锭，锌锭，锌合金，铝棒，电解镍，铅锭现货批发贸易和期货的套期保值，同时还为客户提供包括订单代采，货物质押，仓储物流等业务。</span></p></section></section>', 1, 0, 10, 255, '2021-08-12 17:47:01', '2021-08-12 17:47:01', '2021-08-12 17:47:01', '2023-07-21 13:48:24', '/upload/image/20210812/6114ee125c48c.jpeg', 'null', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'PC', 'zh-CN');
