(211, 24, '秋叶原热烈祝贺国家安防行业标准《安防线缆产品认证实施规则》修订稿评审会圆满召开！', '助人为乐、博爱奉献”--- 秋叶原爱心基金正式成立！', '<section data-role=\"outer\" label=\"Powered by 135editor.com\"><section data-role=\"paragraph\" data-mpa-powered-by=\"yiban.io\" class=\"\"><section style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em; height: 0px; overflow: hidden;\"></section><section style=\"text-align: justify;letter-spacing: 1.5px;line-height: 1.5em;\" class=\"\"><p style=\"font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 16px;\">9月13日，《安防线缆产品认证实施规则》修订稿评审会在广东省惠州市博罗县罗浮山嘉宝田酒店圆满召开！<br/></span></p></section><section style=\"text-align: justify;letter-spacing: 1.5px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><p style=\"font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><br/></p></section><section style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20210915/1631697127481070.jpg\" title=\"1631697127481070.jpg\" alt=\"640.webp.jpg\"/></section><p style=\"text-align: justify;letter-spacing: 1.5px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;letter-spacing: 1.5px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">此次针对安防线缆认证规则，增加了安防线缆接插件认证检验项目，明确型式试验检测样品要求，监督检测抽样的办法，确定所生产的产品符合规定要求的检验试验仪器设备。</span></p><section style=\"text-align: justify;letter-spacing: 1.5px;line-height: 1.5em;\" class=\"\"><p style=\"font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><br/></p></section><section style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.5em; height: 0px; overflow: hidden;\" class=\"\"></section><section style=\"text-align: justify;letter-spacing: 1.5px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><p style=\"font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20210915/1631697137682994.jpg\" title=\"1631697137682994.jpg\" alt=\"2.webp.jpg\"/></p></section><p style=\"text-align: justify;letter-spacing: 1.5px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;letter-spacing: 1.5px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; letter-spacing: 0.5px;\">中国安全技术防范认证中心、公安部第一研究所、深圳市秋叶原实业有限公司、深圳市南士科技股份有限公司、上海爱谱华顿集团电子科技有限公司、浙江万马通信线缆有限公司、广州宇洪科技股份有限公司等国家标准化技术委员会及相关行业领导企业共同参加会议并参与标准审议。</span></p><section style=\"text-align: justify;letter-spacing: 1.5px;line-height: 1.5em;\" class=\"\"><p style=\"font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><br/></p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20210915/1631697148633200.jpg\" title=\"1631697148633200.jpg\" alt=\"30.webp.jpg\"/></p></section><section style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.5em; height: 0px; overflow: hidden;\" class=\"\"></section><p style=\"text-align:center;\"><br/></p></section><p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">《安全技术防范产品自愿性认证实施规则 安防线缆产品》（编号：CSP-V06-001:2017)是由中国安全技术防范认证中心组织制订，经公安部科信局批准实施中国公共安全产品认证（GA认证）的安防产品认证实施规则。自颁布以来，对推动安防线缆标准的贯彻实施，改进产品质量发挥了积极作用。目前，修订后的GA/T 1297-2021《安防线缆》和GA/T 1351-2018《安防线缆接插件》已发布实施，为满足视频监控等安防系统工程对提升线缆和接插件产品质量的需要，组织对安防线缆产品认证实施规则进行了修订，增加了安防线缆接插件产品的认证要求。</span></p><section data-role=\"paragraph\"><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><br/></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20210915/1631697160373242.jpg\" title=\"1631697160373242.jpg\" alt=\"4.webp.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><br/></p></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\"><section style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em; height: 0px; overflow: hidden;\" class=\"\"></section><section style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\" class=\"\"><br/></section></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\"><p style=\"text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">此次召开<span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; line-height: 1.5em; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">的</span>《安防线缆产品认证实施规则》修订稿评审会强化了安防线缆接插件产品安全质量监管，对<span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; line-height: 1.5em; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">信号传输线缆产品的选用、安装等规定了一些原则性的要求，对提升安防线缆接插件产品将有章可循、有标准可依、有设计原则，</span>推动了安防线缆行业健康、可持续发展，对规范安防线缆市场行为起到划时代意义。</span></p><p style=\"letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.5em; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20210915/1631697172825354.jpg\" title=\"1631697172825354.jpg\" alt=\"5.webp.jpg\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; text-align: left; text-indent: 28px; white-space: pre-wrap;\"/></p><section style=\"text-align: justify;letter-spacing: 1.5px;line-height: 1.5em;\" class=\"\"><p style=\"text-indent: 28px; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><br/></p></section><section style=\"text-align: justify;letter-spacing: 1.5px;line-height: 1.5em;\" class=\"\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 28px; white-space: pre-wrap;\">秋叶原</span>作为国内安防线缆企业的杰出代表，全程参与了此次标准审议，将不遗余力，努力做好安防线缆产品认证实施规则的推进者和践行者，成为实施规则的一大助力。</span></section></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\"><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px; text-align: justify; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px; text-align: justify; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20210915/1631697228146293.jpg\" title=\"1631697228146293.jpg\" alt=\"6.webp.jpg\"/></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px; text-align: justify; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; letter-spacing: 0.5px; text-align: justify;\">随着中国安防行业蓬勃发展，安防线缆产品作为重要的信号传输介质，被广泛应用于各大安防系统的连接，并发挥着重要的作用。未来，相信在企业、行业、权威机构共同努力下，秋叶原与整个安防工程线缆行业将会迈向设计专业性、系统可靠性、用户保障性的领域，促进安防系统的稳定性及市场的良性发展。<br/></span></p></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\" class=\"\"><section style=\"text-align: justify;letter-spacing: 1.5px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><br/></section></section><section style=\"line-height: 1.5em; height: 0px; overflow: hidden;\" class=\"\"></section><section style=\"line-height: 1.5em; height: 0px; overflow: hidden;\" class=\"\"></section></section><p><br/></p>', 1, 0, 10, 255, '2021-09-15 17:14:15', '2021-09-15 17:14:15', '2021-09-15 17:14:15', '2023-07-21 13:48:24', '/upload/image/20210915/6141b95f9d28e.jpeg', 'null', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'PC', 'zh-CN'),
(213, 24, '【科普】什么是DP接口', '助人为乐、博爱奉献”--- 秋叶原爱心基金正式成立！', '<section data-role=\"paragraph\" data-mpa-powered-by=\"yiban.io\" class=\"\" style=\"white-space: normal;\"><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 2px; caret-color: red;\">随着显示器技术的不断发展，</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 2px;\">高带宽和高刷新率的线材大受追捧</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 2px; caret-color: red;\">，DP高清线就成了极致影音爱好者首选，电竞发烧友至爱！</span><br/></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 2px; caret-color: red;\"><br/></span></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.75em;\"><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/ueditor/php/upload/image/20210926/1632619590636324.jpg\" title=\"1632619590636324.jpg\" alt=\"微信图片_20210926092613.jpg\"/></p></section><p><section data-role=\"paragraph\" class=\"\" style=\"white-space: normal;\"><p style=\"text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><strong><span style=\"text-indent: 28px;\"><br/></span></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><strong><span style=\"text-indent: 28px;\">DP（DisplayPort）</span></strong><span style=\"text-indent: 28px;\">是一种高清数字显示接口标准，可以连接电脑和显示器，也可以连接电脑和</span>家庭影院<span style=\"text-indent: 28px;\">，是第一个依赖数据包化数据传输技术的显示通信端口。</span></span></p></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\" style=\"white-space: normal;\"><p><br/></p></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\" class=\"\" style=\"white-space: normal;\"><p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1.5px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">DP接口作为DVI的继任者，也</span><span style=\"max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 1px; outline: none 0px !important;\">可以简单理解成HDMI的加强版。它</span><span style=\"caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">在传输视频信号的同时加入对高清音频信号传输的支持，同时支持更高的分辨率和刷新率。在数据传输上，DP使用了“micro-packetised”格式，并具备高度的可扩展性，可以在今后不断加入更多新内容。</span></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1.5px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><br/></span></span></p></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\" class=\"\" style=\"white-space: normal;\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/ueditor/php/upload/image/20210926/1632619550225347.jpg\" title=\"1632619550225347.jpg\" alt=\"O1CN010iIXwb2BiQSyuQvwQ_!!407628372_看图王.jpg\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify;\"/></p></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\" class=\"\" style=\"white-space: normal;\"><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><strong style=\"caret-color: red;\"><br/></strong></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><strong style=\"caret-color: red;\">DP版本发展</strong><br/></span></p></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\" class=\"\" style=\"white-space: normal;\"><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">1.1 带宽10.8Gbps，最高支持 2560*1600 (2K）分辨率（已基本淘汰）</span></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">1.2 带宽21.6Gbps，最高支持 4K（4096*2160）60Hz&nbsp;（最常用）</span></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">1.3 带宽32.4Gbps，最高支持 4K（3840X2160）120hz、5K（5120X2880）60hz、8K（7680X4320）30hz 输出。</span></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">1.4 带宽32.4Gbps，最高支持 8K 级别（7680x4320）的 60Hz 输出，4K 的话则可以上到120Hz。（最新版本）</span></p></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\" style=\"white-space: normal;\"><p><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/ueditor/php/upload/image/20210926/1632619887952053.jpg\" title=\"1632619887952053.jpg\" alt=\"O1CN018pZrDJ1n0PiV18jPa_!!398685027.jpg\"/></p><p><br/></p></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\" class=\"\" style=\"white-space: normal;\"><p style=\"text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">我们在购买DP线的时候会发现DP线的种类很多，按大小分为<strong><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">DP接口和苹果开发的mini DP接口</span></strong>，它们之间又有</span><span style=\"max-inline-size: 100%; outline: 0px; cursor: text; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 0.544px;\">公对公、公对母之分。</span></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"max-inline-size: 100%; outline: 0px; cursor: text; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 0.544px;\"><br/></span></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">常见的是DP公对公高清线，</span><span style=\"max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; caret-color: red; outline: none 0px !important;\">一般用作设备互连用的直连线，也叫视频线，比如电脑输出端接电视输入端；公对母一般用作数据延长线或特殊设备连接线，所以也叫转换线。</span></span></p></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\" style=\"white-space: normal;\"><p><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/ueditor/php/upload/image/20210926/1632619909144046.jpg\" title=\"1632619909144046.jpg\" alt=\"O1CN01latyhh1n0PiV19OzU_!!398685027.jpg\"/></p><p><br/></p></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\" class=\"\" style=\"white-space: normal;\"><p style=\"text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">其实选择正确的DP线并不难，<span style=\"caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">根据自家设备配置情况及自身对游戏、视频输出效果的要求，确认DP线标准即可。如想体验</span><span style=\"caret-color: red;\">8K超清视界，游戏操作如行云流水就选这款<strong>秋叶原1.4版DP高清线</strong>。</span></span></p></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\" class=\"\" style=\"white-space: normal;\"><section style=\"text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; letter-spacing: 1px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">精炼铜芯，多层屏蔽抗干扰，高带宽，满足8K@60Hz、4K@144Hz、2K@165Hz多种刷新率，消除画质撕裂，让画面清晰动人，玩游戏制霸全场。</span></section><p style=\"text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.75em;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"caret-color: red; outline: 0px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">镀金接口具有抗腐蚀、耐拔插、防生锈的效果，<span style=\"outline: 0px; letter-spacing: 0.544px;\">让多次拔插得到有效保护</span>。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"caret-color: red; outline: 0px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">多屏拼接模式、复制模式、拓展模式玩转大屏。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><br/></span></p></section><section style=\"white-space: normal;\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/ueditor/php/upload/image/20210926/1632619935263544.jpg\" title=\"1632619935263544.jpg\" alt=\"微信图片_20210908172801.jpg\"/></p><p><br/></p></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\" style=\"white-space: normal;\"><section data-role=\"paragraph\" class=\"\"><p style=\"letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><strong style=\"caret-color: red;\">使用DP转接器/转换线注意事项：</strong><br/></span></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">当你要连接的输入设备和输出设备中只有一端是DP接口，那在使用转接器/转换线进行连接时就要注意：</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">DP转HDMI可以实现双向转接，传输画面不会失真；</span><br/></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">DP转DVI是单向转接，DP转DVI产品只能DP向DVI转换，DP端接电脑主机显卡，DVI接显示器，反过来用则没有显示；</span></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">DP转VGA，这两种接口不能直接转接，转接器需要添加芯片，但是一般售卖转接器中都是加了芯片的，所以一般不用担心这个问题。</span></p></section></section></p>', 1, 0, 10, 255, '2021-09-26 09:35:55', '2021-09-26 09:35:55', '2021-09-26 09:35:55', '2023-07-21 13:48:24', '/upload/image/20210926/614fce77d475b.jpeg', 'null', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'PC', 'zh-CN'),
(215, 24, '【分析】如何挑选网络面板', '助人为乐、博爱奉献”--- 秋叶原爱心基金正式成立！', '<section data-role=\"outer\" label=\"Powered by 135editor.com\"><section data-role=\"outer\" label=\"Powered by 135editor.com\" data-mpa-powered-by=\"yiban.io\" class=\"\"><p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\"><strong><span style=\"caret-color: red; color: rgb(255, 76, 65);\">网络面板</span></strong><span style=\"caret-color: red; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\">是指应用于工作区布线子系统，<span style=\"text-align: start; text-indent: 28px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">适合多类型模块安装的一类布线产品，</span></span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\">它的主要作用是用以固定模块，保护信息出口处的线缆。</span></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63); letter-spacing: 1px;\"><br/></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"></span><span style=\"text-align: start; text-indent: 28px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">网络面板对于布线系统来说，不是主要影响性能的产品部件，</span>但却<span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: start; text-indent: 28px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">是仅有的几个外露在墙体</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">表面</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: start; text-indent: 28px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">的产品之一，其性能与美观直接影响着整体布线的效果。</span></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: start; text-indent: 28px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></span></span></p><section style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.75em;\"><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/ueditor/php/upload/image/20210930/1632970374135400.jpg\" title=\"1632970374135400.jpg\" alt=\"微信图片_20210922161335.jpg\"/></section><p style=\"text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63); letter-spacing: 1px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63); letter-spacing: 1px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">如今人们对家的期待延伸到对装修近乎完美的苛刻，要求无差别融入整体装修风格，才能看得舒心，用得舒心，在<span style=\"caret-color: red;\">选择网络面板时对外观和其质量性能都有着高要求。</span></span></p><section style=\"text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.75em;\"><p style=\"caret-color: red; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); letter-spacing: 1px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><br/></p><p style=\"caret-color: red; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); letter-spacing: 1px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/ueditor/php/upload/image/20210930/1632970392681648.jpg\" title=\"1632970392681648.jpg\" alt=\"O1CN011n0PUTttbgnrX5o_!!398685027.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"caret-color: red; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); letter-spacing: 1px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><br/></p></section><img src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/P5z9Rt3xHTqiaibN4icJN1iaCR0wB5zW3I7fVk0icicwmJmC3arZBwcVjZXycicS6VaRnRoyheq27icXtDibKYIgOzCdq9A/640?wx_fmt=png\" data-type=\"png\" data-width=\"100%\" data-ratio=\"0.6216216216216216\" data-w=\"37\"/><p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><strong>那网络面板应该怎么选呢？</strong></span></p><section data-role=\"paragraph\"><section style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><br/></section></section><section style=\"text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><strong><span style=\"caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); color: rgb(63, 63, 63); text-shadow: rgb(255, 0, 0) 2px 2px 10px;\">风格：</span></strong></span></section><section style=\"text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); color: rgb(63, 63, 63); letter-spacing: 1px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">网络面板主要和布线的美观有关，在选择款式和颜色应该与装修风格相符合，如果装修风格整体色调是浅色，可以选择白色、香槟金等浅色的网络面板。</span></section><section style=\"text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.75em;\"><br/></section><section style=\"text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63); text-shadow: rgb(255, 0, 0) 2px 2px 10px;\">外表：</span></strong></span></section><section style=\"text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63); letter-spacing: 1px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">表面光滑，摸起来没有凹凸不平的感觉，开关拨动的手感轻巧且不紧涩。</span></section><section style=\"text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.75em;\"><br/></section><section style=\"text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63); text-shadow: rgb(255, 0, 0) 2px 2px 10px;\">性能：</span></strong></span></section><section style=\"text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">在网络面板之下的网络模块是连接网线的核心，可以影响到整个布线系统的性能。选用金属屏蔽模块的网络面板，经过特殊抗氧化处理，耐腐蚀性强，有效抵抗电磁干扰，经久耐用，保证信号传输长效稳定。<br/></span></section><section style=\"text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.75em;\"><br/></section><section style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63); letter-spacing: 1px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><strong><span style=\"text-shadow: rgb(255, 0, 0) 2px 2px 10px;\">类别：</span></strong></span></section><p style=\"text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">在确定好装修布线方案后要根据网线类别来选择与之对应的网络面板，才能达到其最佳传输性能。</span></p><section style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;\"><br/></section><section class=\"\" style=\"text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63); text-shadow: rgb(255, 0, 0) 2px 2px 10px;\">品牌：</span></strong><br/></span></section><p style=\"text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); text-indent: 0em; caret-color: red;\">产品的质量会对家庭的安全问题、设备的正常使用、甚至生活的便利程度造成影响，无论是网线、<span style=\"text-align: left;\">网络面板还是其他产品</span>，都应该选用可靠性高的知名品牌，如</span><span style=\"text-indent: 0em; caret-color: red; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(255, 76, 65);\"><strong>秋叶原</strong></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63); text-indent: 0em; caret-color: red;\">作为传输行业著名品牌，</span><span style=\"caret-color: red; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); text-indent: 0em; outline-style: initial;\">在售后、质量、价格都是值得信赖的。</span></span></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span style=\"caret-color: red; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); text-indent: 0em; outline-style: initial;\"><br/></span></span></span></p><section class=\"\" style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.75em;\"></section><section style=\"text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"caret-color: red; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); text-indent: 0em; outline-style: initial; text-align: left; letter-spacing: 1px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">以上就是选择网络面板应该注意的地方，同时，<span style=\"text-indent: 0em; outline-style: initial;\">网络面板</span>的位置和数量对于室内装修的便捷性和美观性起着重要的作用，大家购买之前一定要根据网点和家具的<span style=\"text-indent: 0em; outline-style: initial;\">位置</span>规划来确认进行。</span></section></section></section><p><br/></p>', 1, 0, 10, 255, '2021-09-30 10:54:44', '2021-09-30 10:54:44', '2021-09-30 10:54:44', '2023-07-21 13:48:24', '/upload/image/20210930/615526f047419.jpeg', 'null', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'PC', 'zh-CN'),
(217, 24, '【分析】怎样延长HDMI传输距离', '助人为乐、博爱奉献”--- 秋叶原爱心基金正式成立！', '<section data-role=\"outer\" label=\"Powered by 135editor.com\" data-mpa-powered-by=\"yiban.io\" class=\"\"><p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1.5px;\"><span style=\"caret-color: red; letter-spacing: 0.544px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">HDMI作为当前最主流的音视频接口，势头如日中天，但<span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px;\">一</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px;\">般的HDMI线</span>传输距离在30米以内，而在实际部署中，受场地布局及设备体积影响，经常会出现用线距离超出30米的情况，那怎样延长HDMI的传输距离呢？</span><br/></p><section data-role=\"paragraph\"><p><br/></p></section><p><strong data-original-title=\"\" title=\"\">1.</strong><strong style=\"caret-color: red;\">HDMI 延长器</strong></p><p><br/></p><section data-role=\"paragraph\" class=\"\"><p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1.5px;\"><span style=\"text-indent: 28px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">HDMI延长器是用来延长信号的器件，具有<span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px;\">一个发射端，一个接收端，</span><span style=\"caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">通常用于长距离直连线材无法满足传输要求的情况，一般是为了确保信号长距离无衰减的传输而设计，因此多是有源的。</span></span></p></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\" class=\"\"><p><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/ueditor/php/upload/image/20211013/1634089866455593.jpg\" title=\"1634089866455593.jpg\" alt=\"O1CN01Y0YvEU1n0Pc1pM9YE_!!398685027 (1).jpg\"/></p><p><br/></p></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\" class=\"\"><p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1.5px;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">HDMI延长器发射端与接收端之间采用【网线、无线、电力、网桥、同轴、光纤】等传输介质进行连接。<span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px;\">目前用途最广的一种是</span><strong style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; background-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;HDMI网线延长器&nbsp;</span></strong><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px;\">，在</span><span style=\"max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; text-indent: 28px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 1px;\">发射端与接收端中间使用Cat6/Cat6A网线连接延伸，</span><span style=\"max-inline-size: 100%; outline: 0px; cursor: text; text-indent: 28px; caret-color: red; letter-spacing: 1px;\">确保信号长距离无衰减传输</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-indent: 28px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">。</span></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1.5px;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1.5px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); outline: 0px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">常见的</span><strong><span style=\"outline: 0px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; background-color: rgb(255, 76, 65); font-size: 14px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;<strong style=\"letter-spacing: 1.5px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; letter-spacing: 0.544px;\">秋</span></strong>叶原HDMI网线延长器&nbsp;</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); outline: 0px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">有60米、120米、150米<span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">的</span>规格，<span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">在成本上与HDMI线材对比价格更低，是长距离传输中经济实惠之选。且容错成本低，整条传输线路中单独一个配件损坏都可以更新替换使用。</span></span><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; caret-color: red; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"></span></p></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\"><p><br/></p></section><p><strong data-original-title=\"\" title=\"\">2.</strong><strong style=\"caret-color: red;\">HDMI 光纤线&nbsp;</strong></p><p><br/></p><section data-role=\"paragraph\" class=\"\"><p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1.5px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">HDMI光纤线堪称长距离传输的未来，它</span>以光纤作为传输介质，<span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">不受外部电磁干扰，</span><span style=\"outline: 0px; letter-spacing: 1px; caret-color: red;\">信号传输衰减几乎为零，可以轻松做到百米级的超长距离传输。</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); outline: 0px; letter-spacing: 1px; caret-color: red; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1.5px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; letter-spacing: 1px; caret-color: red;\"><br/></span></span></p></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\" class=\"\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/ueditor/php/upload/image/20211013/1634089807104719.jpg\" title=\"1634089807104719.jpg\" alt=\"微信图片_20211012135817.jpg\"/></p></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\" class=\"\"><p style=\"text-align: justify; outline: 0px; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1.5px; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; letter-spacing: 1px; caret-color: red;\"><br/></span></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; outline: 0px; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1.5px; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; letter-spacing: 1px; caret-color: red;\">秋叶原</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1.5px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong><span style=\"outline: 0px; letter-spacing: 1px; caret-color: red; background-color: rgb(255, 76, 65);\">&nbsp;第三代光纤复合HDMI高清线&nbsp;</span></strong></span></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; letter-spacing: 1px; caret-color: red;\">,开创</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; letter-spacing: 1px; caret-color: red;\">150米超长光电智慧，领衔新标杆！但它</span>不同于铜线HDMI两端可以任意连接，光纤HDMI线是有方向性的，发射端（source）和接收端（display）不能弄反，在布线的时候一定要注意。</span></p></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\" class=\"\"><p><br/></p></section><p><strong data-original-title=\"\" title=\"\">3.</strong><strong style=\"caret-color: red;\">HDMI 延长线&nbsp;</strong></p><p><br/></p><section data-role=\"paragraph\" class=\"\"><p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1.5px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">短线加长，不受“线”制。HDMI公对母延长线可以用来延长传输距离，另外，针对居家壁挂电视机及带有HDMI接口的台式机插拔不方便的问题，可以将HDMI母口延伸出来，使用更加简单方便！</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1.5px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><br/></span></p></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\" class=\"\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/ueditor/php/upload/image/20211013/1634089823894270.jpg\" title=\"1634089823894270.jpg\" alt=\"TB2_nImAf9TBuNjy1zbXXXpepXa_!!398685027.jpg\"/></p></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\" class=\"\"><p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1.5px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><br/></span></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1.5px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\">以上就是延长HDMI传输距离的3种方法，</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; caret-color: red;\">大家可以根据设备和自身需求制定合理的方案<span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px;\">来选</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px;\">择</span>产品</span><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 14px; caret-color: red;\">哦~</span></span></p></section></section>', 1, 0, 10, 255, '2021-10-13 09:53:38', '2021-10-13 09:53:38', '2021-10-13 09:53:38', '2023-07-21 13:48:24', '/upload/image/20211013/61663c1954022.jpeg', 'null', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'PC', 'zh-CN'),
(219, 24, '【新品首发】秋叶原新型石墨烯屏蔽HDMI线即将震撼来袭', '助人为乐、博爱奉献”--- 秋叶原爱心基金正式成立！', '<p data-track=\"1\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">随着科技和互联网的发展，大量的电子设备在工作时会产生大量不同波长、不同频率的电磁波，造成干扰，这对设备自身和信号传输线材的电磁屏蔽材料提出了更高的要求。</p><p data-track=\"1\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><br/></p><p data-track=\"2\">而HDMI作为当前最主流的音视频数字接口，其线材的优劣会直接影响信号的传输效果，因此，HDMI高清线的电磁屏蔽材料至关重要。</p><p data-track=\"2\"><br/></p><p data-track=\"2\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20211020/1634692790580483.jpg\" title=\"1634692790580483.jpg\" alt=\"微信图片_202110191731592.jpg\"/></p><p data-track=\"2\"><br/></p><p data-track=\"3\">作为高性能音视频线材和配件的著名品牌，<strong>秋叶原</strong>为了能够把HDMI线的音频和视频传输性能提升到另一个新高度，在线材的设计上会不断地进行细节上的改良，敢为行业先，特别采用<strong>新材料之王石墨烯</strong>加码HDMI技术研发生产了<strong>新型石墨烯屏蔽HDMI线</strong>。</p><p data-track=\"3\"><br/></p><p data-track=\"3\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20211020/1634692832164584.jpg\" title=\"1634692832164584.jpg\" alt=\"640.webp (1).jpg\"/></p><p data-track=\"4\"><br/></p><p data-track=\"4\">（如图）线材外护套内壁那层薄薄黑色就是石墨烯屏蔽层，虽然很薄，但是能达到优于传统金属编织的屏蔽效果，而且因为石墨烯的自身特性线身可以做的更细，更软，提高线材的弯曲性能和柔韧性，从而延长HDMI线的使用寿命。</p><p data-track=\"4\"><br/></p><p data-track=\"5\"><strong>什么是石墨烯</strong></p><p data-track=\"5\"><strong><br/></strong></p><p data-track=\"6\">石墨烯是作为一种具有颠覆性、革命性的新材料，是一种碳六元环组成的蜂窝状二维纳米材料，sp²杂化碳原子贡献的可自由移动的电子赋予了石墨烯优异的导电性和导热性，能有效降低材料密度并增强电磁屏蔽性能，在电磁屏蔽领域拥有广泛的应用价值。</p><p data-track=\"6\"><br/></p><p data-track=\"6\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20211020/1634692854653297.png\" title=\"1634692854653297.png\" alt=\"t01f09d21b6b0e159c9.png\"/></p><p data-track=\"6\"><br/></p><p data-track=\"7\">单片48.3μm 的蜂窝状多孔石墨烯材料，在10 GHz时的电磁屏蔽性能大约是40dB，此时它能屏蔽 99.99% 的入射电磁波；<strong>当把该材料堆叠到 6 层后，电磁屏蔽性能可达80dB，并能衰减 99.999999% 的入射电磁波。</strong></p><p data-track=\"8\">其优异的光学、电学、力学特性，在材料学、微纳加工、能源、生物医学和药物传递等方面具有重要的应用前景，被认为是一种未来革命性的材料。</p><p data-track=\"9\"><strong><br/></strong></p><p data-track=\"9\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20211020/1634692872844319.jpg\" title=\"1634692872844319.jpg\" alt=\"微信图片_20211019173159.jpg\"/></strong></p><p data-track=\"9\"><strong><br/></strong></p><p data-track=\"9\"><strong>新型石墨烯屏蔽HDMI线产品特点</strong></p><p data-track=\"10\">1、带宽扩充到了18Gbps，支持即插即用和热插拔，支持3840×2160分辨率。</p><p data-track=\"11\">2、在音频方面支持最多32个声道，以及最高1536kHz采样率。</p><p data-track=\"12\">3、对HDR格式传输的支持，能够显著增强图像质量。</p><p data-track=\"13\">4、采用新型石墨烯屏蔽材料替代传统编织加铝箔屏蔽降低人工成本的同时屏蔽性能更佳。</p><p data-track=\"14\">5、采用新型石墨烯屏蔽材料的产品相较传统编织加铝箔屏蔽，线身更柔软，手感更佳。</p><p data-track=\"15\">6、石墨烯屏蔽材料生产的线材比编织生产的线材在高频800MHz时EMI余量更大，差距明显（如图）。</p><p data-track=\"15\"><br/></p><p data-track=\"15\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20211020/1634692923592389.jpg\" title=\"1634692923592389.jpg\" alt=\"640.webp (2).jpg\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" data-track=\"16\"><strong>秋叶原新型石墨烯屏蔽材料样品测试</strong></p><p data-track=\"16\"><strong><br/></strong></p><p data-track=\"16\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20211020/1634692933533449.jpg\" title=\"1634692933533449.jpg\" alt=\"6401.webp.jpg\"/></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" data-track=\"17\"><strong>秋叶原传统屏蔽材料样品测试</strong></p><p data-track=\"17\"><strong><br/></strong></p><p data-track=\"18\">经过进一步的研发，不断提高技术壁垒，新型石墨烯屏蔽HDMI线相比传统的HDMI线均有显著的优势，不断带给人们新的惊喜，而且线材可以做的更细，更软，有着广阔的前景。</p><p data-track=\"18\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" data-track=\"19\"><strong>秋叶原新型石墨烯屏蔽HDMI线即将震撼上市</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" data-track=\"20\"><strong>敬请期待！</strong></p><p data-track=\"20\"><strong><br/></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20211020/1634692947462567.jpg\" title=\"1634692947462567.jpg\" alt=\"微信图片_202110191731591.jpg\"/></p><p><br/></p>', 1, 0, 10, 255, '2021-10-20 09:23:40', '2021-10-20 09:23:40', '2021-10-20 09:23:40', '2023-07-21 13:48:24', '/upload/image/20211020/616f6f9842d69.jpeg', 'null', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'PC', 'zh-CN');
