inkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;\"><br/></p><section data-id=\"98767\" class=\"_135editor\"><section style=\"margin:10px auto;\"><section style=\"background-image: url(&quot;https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/UH19PdPjIicsKWpSlR7rOV0o28ZeD5xBkBB2zg6aJYicBoRUCxGaiaelibP6BpqNnq797KZDTuVCCwicahkc5B0ib81A/640?wx_fmt=gif&quot;);background-size: cover;background-repeat: no-repeat;background-position: center top;padding: 3px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><section style=\"background-color: #ffffff;padding: 1em;box-sizing: border-box;\"><section style=\"line-height: 1.75em;letter-spacing: 1.5px;font-size: 14px;\"><section data-autoskip=\"1\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><section data-role=\"title\" data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"106349\" class=\"_135editor\"><section style=\"text-align: center;margin: 10px auto;\"><section style=\"display:flex;align-items: center;\"><section style=\"display: inline-block;margin-right: 10px;\"><section style=\"background-color: #f84541;padding: 5px 15px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><section data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"font-size: 16px;color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>集团公司</strong></span></section></section></section><section style=\"flex: 1;\"><section data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: #f84541;text-align: left;margin-left: 5px;\"><br/></section><section style=\"box-sizing:border-box;width: 100%;height: 1px;background-color: #f96a67;margin-top: 3px;overflow: hidden;\" data-width=\"100%\"><br/></section></section></section></section></section><section style=\"text-align: justify;text-indent: 0em;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63); letter-spacing: 2px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">广东前海秋叶原集团是一家以线缆生态链、产业园投资运营与互联网+布局，集研发、生产、销售及园区运营服务于一体的<span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">国家级高新技术企业集团，</span>“Choseal秋叶原”是中国驰名商标，主营智能工程线缆、高品质影音线缆、IT数码周边配套智能连接产品，为“现代品味生活、智能家居以及智慧城市”用户提供工程项目系统集成解决方案以及上下游产品供应服务。</span><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"></span></section><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent: 0em;line-height: 1.5em;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent: 0em;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">旗下前海中融国际投资控股集团专业进行产业园投资、运营管理及服务于实体经济的平台打造，运营 “梦科园”系列新兴产业园及产业综合体项目。</span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent: 0em;line-height: 1.5em;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent: 0em;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63); text-indent: 0em; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">秋叶原始终凭借优质的产品与服务，完善的管理体系，坚持“以科技和服务创造美好生活”和“塑造秋叶原百年品牌”的发展理念，让企业得到了长足的发展，在未来，秋叶原将不断努力耕耘，向全世界展现秋叶原集团的成长风采。</span><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63); text-indent: 0em; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"></span></p></section></section></section></section></section></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\"><p><br/></p></section><p style=\"text-align:justify; outline: 0px; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1.5px;\">深圳，作为中国改革开放的前沿阵地，“深圳500强企业”榜单的发布，对深圳全面建设粤港澳大湾区和中国特色社会主义先行示范区有着极强的示范效应和积极影响。<span style=\"letter-spacing: 1.5px;\">此次入选“2021深圳500强企业”，是深圳市委市政</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1.5px;\">府及社会各界对秋叶原</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-indent: 34px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">积极开拓创新、砥砺奋进的重要见证和高度认可</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1.5px;\">。</span></span></span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify; outline: 0px; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align:justify; outline: 0px; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20211101/1635732464667441.jpg\" title=\"1635732464667441.jpg\" alt=\"微信图片_20211029155118.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"text-align:justify; outline: 0px; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align:justify; outline: 0px; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">在新的历史时期，秋叶原将<span style=\"outline: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; letter-spacing: 0.533333px; text-indent: 34px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;;\">继续秉承</span><span style=\"font-size: 14.6667px; letter-spacing: 0.533333px; text-indent: 34px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;;\">“以科技和服务创造美好生活”的企业使命，</span>不断开拓创新，锐意进取，进一步提升核心竞争力，勇当科技排头兵，积极投身于粤港澳大湾区建设和深圳先行示范区建设的热潮中，为推进深圳经济发展作出更大贡献。</span></p></section></section></section>', 1, 0, 10, 255, '2021-11-01 10:08:55', '2021-11-01 10:08:55', '2021-11-01 10:08:55', '2023-07-21 13:48:24', '/upload/image/20211101/617f4c33942f5.jpeg', 'null', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'PC', 'zh-CN'),
(222, 24, '【分析】线材光纤化有什么优势', '助人为乐、博爱奉献”--- 秋叶原爱心基金正式成立！', '<section data-role=\"paragraph\" class=\"\" style=\"white-space: normal;\"><p style=\"text-align: justify; vertical-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 14px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">随着8K/4K影音应用与数码相机、摄影机相继挑战超高分辨率记录功能，对于现有的传输接口性能要求也越来越高，</span><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 14px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">高速传输接口承载的资料传输量持续挑战铜缆线材的物理极限。</span><br/></span></p><section data-role=\"paragraph\" class=\"\"><p style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><br/></p></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\" class=\"\"><p style=\"text-align: justify; vertical-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"caret-color: red;\">因此影音产品对于由8K/4K UHDTV带起的高速传输接口集成风潮，如HDMI/DP等，</span>虽在传输效能获得跃进式地大幅改善，</span><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 14px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">但在长距离布设应用状况下，常用的</span><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 14px; max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; caret-color: red; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; outline: none 0px !important;\">铜芯特性并不利于长距离高速传送！</span></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; vertical-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.75em;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; vertical-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.75em;\"><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/ueditor/php/upload/image/20211108/1636335218576936.jpg\" title=\"1636335218576936.jpg\" alt=\"O1CN01dMrSkz1n0Pb52bJZi_!!398685027.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; vertical-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 14px; caret-color: red; letter-spacing: 1px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; vertical-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 14px; caret-color: red; letter-spacing: 1px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">铜缆传输速度与信号的辨识度都会因为距离拉长而受影响，如果搭配中继器等设备改善信号质量，会使传输成本暴增，同时对接口传输质量与稳定性也会造成影响！因此，<span style=\"caret-color: red; text-align: left;\">要求兼具传输距离与传输性能，AOC线材解决方案才能满足应用需求。</span></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; vertical-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.75em;\"><br/></p></section></section><p><section data-role=\"paragraph\" style=\"white-space: normal;\"><p style=\"text-align: justify; vertical-align: inherit; outline: 0px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.75em; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 14px; outline: 0px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">秋叶原作为影音连接线行业领军企业，下设秋叶原线缆研究院特研发出以光纤为传输介质，完美化解困扰业界远距离高速传输问题，实现</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(255, 76, 65); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;\">百米级以上</span></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 14px; outline: 0px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;\">超长距离传输视频信号的</span><span style=\"outline: 0px;\">秋叶原新一代光纤系列产品隆重面市，一起来看看吧！</span></span></span></p></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\" class=\"\" style=\"white-space: normal;\"><p style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><br/></p></section></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; vertical-align: inherit;\"><strong>第三代光纤复合HDMI高清线</strong></p><p><section data-role=\"paragraph\" class=\"\" style=\"white-space: normal;\"><p style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><br/></p></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\" class=\"\" style=\"white-space: normal; height: 0px; overflow: hidden;\"></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\" style=\"white-space: normal;\"><p style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/ueditor/php/upload/image/20211108/1636335189237358.jpg\" title=\"1636335189237358.jpg\" alt=\"微信图片_20211014160757.jpg\"/></p></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\" style=\"white-space: normal;\"><p style=\"text-align: justify; vertical-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; vertical-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">具有18Gbps的传输带宽，支持真4K、给你震撼3D视效，<span style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;\">画面显示时能做到色彩自然，明亮鲜明，细节层次感清晰，<span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">实现150米近乎0衰减，</span></span>打破超长距离信号传输衰减束缚。匠心呈现，“光”耀未来！</span></p></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\" style=\"white-space: normal;\"><p style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><br/></p></section></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; vertical-align: inherit;\"><strong>蓝光系列光纤DP高清线</strong></p><p><section data-role=\"paragraph\" style=\"white-space: normal;\"><p style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><br/></p></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\" style=\"white-space: normal; height: 0px; overflow: hidden;\"></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\" style=\"white-space: normal;\"><p style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/ueditor/php/upload/image/20211108/1636335169313439.jpg\" title=\"1636335169313439.jpg\" alt=\"微信图片_20211019165646.jpg\"/></p></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\" style=\"white-space: normal;\"><p style=\"text-align: justify; vertical-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; vertical-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">光电DP1.4 模组/AOC 产品采用光纤传输高速音视频信号，电子线传输低速控制信号，线材整体轻便，产品抗电磁干扰好，产品符合 DP1.4 协议规范，满足 8K 高清连接需求,传输距离最高可达150米无损耗传输。</span></p></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\" style=\"white-space: normal;\"><p style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><br/></p></section></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; vertical-align: inherit;\"><strong>蓝光系列光纤DVI高清线</strong></p><p><section data-role=\"paragraph\" style=\"white-space: normal;\"><p style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><br/></p></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\" class=\"\" style=\"white-space: normal; height: 0px; overflow: hidden;\"></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\" style=\"white-space: normal;\"><p style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/ueditor/php/upload/image/20211108/1636335137916469.jpg\" title=\"1636335137916469.jpg\" alt=\"微信图片_202106181046314.jpg\"/></p></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\" class=\"\" style=\"white-space: normal;\"><p style=\"text-align: justify; vertical-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); letter-spacing: 1px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; vertical-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); letter-spacing: 1px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">光电DVI模组/AOC解决传统铜缆在DVI信号传输过程中信号衰减兼容性等问题，支持1080P，传输距离最高可达200米无损耗传输，高速信号通过4条多模光纤进行传输，具有良好的抗干扰性能，线材整体轻便，支持热插拔，低功耗，无需外部电源驱动。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; vertical-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.75em;\"><br/></p></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\" class=\"\" style=\"white-space: normal;\"><section data-role=\"paragraph\"><p style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><strong>蓝光系列光纤HDMI-DVI转换线</strong></p></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\" class=\"\"><br/></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\" class=\"\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); outline: 0px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">同时，秋叶原线缆研究院还攻破了200米超长距离</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(255, 76, 65); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;\">光纤</strong><strong style=\"outline: 0px;\">HDMI-DVI<strong style=\"outline: 0px;\">、</strong><strong style=\"outline: 0px;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;\">DVI-HDMI</strong></strong>转换线</strong></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); outline: 0px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">，可切实实现多接口不同使用需求，真正摆脱传输接口的限制。</span></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\" class=\"\"><br/></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\" class=\"\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"></span></section></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\" class=\"\" style=\"white-space: normal;\"><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/ueditor/php/upload/image/20211108/1636335089450287.jpg\" title=\"1636335089450287.jpg\" alt=\"HDMI.jpg\"/></section></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; vertical-align: inherit;\"><strong><br/></strong></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; vertical-align: inherit;\"><strong>蓝光系列光纤DVI-HDMI转换线</strong></p><p><section data-role=\"paragraph\" class=\"\" style=\"white-space: normal;\"><p style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><br/></p></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\" class=\"\" style=\"white-space: normal;\"><p style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/ueditor/php/upload/image/20211108/1636335050823970.jpg\" title=\"1636335050823970.jpg\" alt=\"dvi.jpg\"/></p></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\" class=\"\" style=\"white-space: normal;\"><p style=\"text-align: justify; vertical-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); letter-spacing: 1px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; color: rgb(255, 76, 65);\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;\"><br/></strong></span></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; vertical-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); letter-spacing: 1px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; color: rgb(255, 76, 65);\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;\">光纤</strong><strong style=\"outline: 0px;\">HDMI-DVI<strong style=\"outline: 0px;\">、</strong><strong style=\"outline: 0px;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;\">DVI-HDMI</strong></strong>转换线</strong></span>，支持1080P视频格式并向下兼容1080i/720P，最高传输速率1.65Gbps.传输距离最高可达200米无损耗传输，高速信号通过4条多模光纤进行传输，具有良好的抗干扰性能，线材整体轻便，低功耗，无需外部电源驱动。</span></p></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\" class=\"\" style=\"white-space: normal;\"><p style=\"text-align: justify; vertical-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63); letter-spacing: 1px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; font-size: 14px;\">光纤与铜是两种常见的传输介质，两者都具备抗干扰性和良好的保密性，但对比之下，</span><span style=\"outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.1px;\">光纤具有传输速率高、传输距离长、能耗低、使用方便等诸多优点，对于传输线缆光纤化需求也在逐渐增强。</span></span></p></section></p>', 1, 0, 10, 255, '2021-11-08 09:51:35', '2021-11-08 09:51:35', '2021-11-08 09:51:35', '2023-07-21 13:48:24', '/upload/image/20211108/6188829786a03.jpeg', 'null', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'PC', 'zh-CN');
