rc=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20211203/1638497376859987.jpg\" title=\"1638497376859987.jpg\" alt=\"微信图片_20211130135850.jpg\"/></span></p></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\"><p style=\"vertical-align:inherit;\"><br/></p></section><section data-role=\"title\" data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"107008\" class=\"_135editor\"><section style=\"text-align: center;margin: 10px auto;\"><section style=\"display: flex;justify-content: center;align-items: center;\"><section style=\"box-sizing:border-box;width: 18px;height: 18px;background-color: rgb(249, 215, 85);border-radius: 50%;margin-right: -9px;flex-shrink: 0;transform: rotate(0deg);-webkit-transform: rotate(0deg);-moz-transform: rotate(0deg);-ms-transform: rotate(0deg);-o-transform: rotate(0deg);\"><section style=\"font-size: 14px;letter-spacing: 1.5px;color: #fff;line-height: 18px;\"><p style=\"vertical-align: inherit;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><strong data-original-title=\"\" title=\"\" data-num=\"6\">3</strong></span></p></section></section><section style=\"display: inline-block;\"><section style=\"background-color: rgb(237, 77, 66); padding: 5px 20px; box-sizing: border-box;\"><section data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1.5px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><p style=\"vertical-align: inherit;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">看网卡</span></p></section></section></section></section></section></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\"><p style=\"vertical-align:inherit;\"><br/></p></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\"><p style=\"vertical-align: inherit;letter-spacing: 1.5px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\">如果家里电脑的网卡不</span><strong><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\">支持千兆宽带</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\">，也是不能使用千兆网络的。</span></span></p><p style=\"vertical-align: inherit;letter-spacing: 1.5px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><br/></p><p style=\"vertical-align:inherit;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20211203/1638497392103293.png\" title=\"1638497392103293.png\" alt=\"微信图片_20211130162544.png\"/></p><p style=\"vertical-align:inherit;\"><br/></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><strong data-brushtype=\"text\">如何查看电脑的网卡</strong></span></p><p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/JaFvPvvA2J3MKYVlmXC32WtRJEYsPM9zPnJkV1fTFuQHlp5RfDMTFYxuCuQwLSPIWsa9uaW9fnAqO9cEJg31eQ/640?wx_fmt=png\" data-type=\"png\" data-width=\"100%\" data-ratio=\"1.0344827586206897\" data-w=\"29\" style=\"vertical-align:inherit;\"/></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">一、打开设备管理器；</span></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">二、点击展开网络适配器，如果为千兆网卡，会含有这些字符：Gigabit、GBE、10/100/1000M、RTL8169。</span></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">如果是含Fast Ethernet、10/100、FE等字符，则为百兆网卡。</span></p></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\"><p style=\"vertical-align:inherit;\"><br/></p><section data-role=\"title\" data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"107008\" class=\"_135editor\"><section style=\"text-align: center;margin: 10px auto;\"><section style=\"display: flex;justify-content: center;align-items: center;\"><section style=\"box-sizing:border-box;width: 18px;h