55, 255); letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">它的主要作用是用以固定模块，保护信息出口处的线缆。</span></span></p><p style=\"vertical-align:inherit;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"vertical-align: inherit; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20211203/1638497494513168.jpg\" title=\"1638497494513168.jpg\" alt=\"微信图片_20210922161335.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"vertical-align:inherit;\"><br/></p><p style=\"vertical-align:inherit;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">在网络面板之下，它的正经搭配者——网络模块，会对整个布线系统的性能会起到重要影响，所以即使升级了千兆宽带也要注意选择相对应的千兆面板和模块。</span></p><p style=\"vertical-align:inherit;\"><br/></p></section><section data-role=\"title\" data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"107008\" class=\"_135editor\"><section style=\"text-align: center;margin: 10px auto;\"><section style=\"display: flex;justify-content: center;align-items: center;\"><section style=\"box-sizing:border-box;width: 18px;height: 18px;background-color: rgb(249, 215, 85);border-radius: 50%;margin-right: -9px;flex-shrink: 0;transform: rotate(0deg);-webkit-transform: rotate(0deg);-moz-transform: rotate(0deg);-ms-transform: rotate(0deg);-o-transform: rotate(0deg);\"><section style=\"font-size: 14px;letter-spacing: 1.5px;color: #fff;line-height: 18px;\"><p style=\"vertical-align: inherit;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><strong data-original-title=\"\" title=\"\" data-num=\"7\">5</strong></span></p></section></section><section style=\"display: inline-block;\"><section style=\"background-color: rgb(237, 77, 66); padding: 5px 20px; box-sizing: border-box;\"><section data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1.5px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><p style=\"vertical-align: inherit;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">看网线</span></p></section></section></section></section></section></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\"><p style=\"vertical-align:inherit;\"><br/></p></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\"><p style=\"text-align:justify;vertical-align: inherit;letter-spacing: 1.5px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.544px;\">网线作为网络设备之间的传输通道，也是影响网速的重要因素。目前市面上网线种类有很多，</span><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\">要想完美传输千兆网络</span>要看<strong>宽带光猫与路由器</strong>之间的连接网线是不是六类及以上网线。</span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;vertical-align: inherit;letter-spacing: 1.5px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center; vertical-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20211203/1638497464727302.jpg\" title=\"1638497464727302.jpg\" alt=\"640.webp.jpg\"/></span></p></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\"><p style=\"text-align:center;vertical-align:inherit;\"><br/></p><p style=\"vertical-align: inherit;letter-spacing: 1.5px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; outline: 0px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; color: rgb(255, 41, 65);\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; outline: none 0px !important;\">六类网线</span></strong></span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); outline: 0px; max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text;\">的传输频率为250Mhz，适用于传输速率高于1Gbps的应用，它</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; caret-color: red; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); letter-spacing: 0.5px; outline-style: initial;\">的传输速率能够提供高于超五类2.5倍的高速带宽，能“真正有保证”地运用于千兆以太网。</span></span></p><p style=\"vertical-align: inherit;letter-spacing: 1.5px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"caret-color: red; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); letter-spacing: 0.5px; outline-style: initial; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"vertical-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://www.choseal.cn/ueditor/php/upload/image/20211203/1638497435292181.jpg\" title=\"1638497435292181.jpg\" alt=\"微信图片_20211130172213.jpg\" style=\"text-align: center; white-space: normal; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px;\"/></p><p style=\"vertical-align: inherit;letter-spacing: 1.5px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(76, 70, 70); letter-spacing: 0.544px; caret-color: red; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"vertical-align: inherit;letter-spacing: 1.5px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(76, 70, 70); letter-spacing: 0.544px; caret-color: red;\">网络设备不带劲，就像拖拉机上高速，做啥努力都是白搭！所以，家庭用户在升级了千兆网络后，</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; caret-color: red; outline-style: initial; letter-spacing: 0.5px;\">不论是</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; caret-color: red; outline-style: initial; letter-spacing: 0.5px; color: rgb(255, 41, 65);\"><strong style=\"outline-style: initial;\">接插件、线缆到链路和信道</strong></span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; caret-color: red; outline-style: initial; letter-spacing: 0.5px;\">全部满足千兆的性能要求，<span style=\"font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(76, 70, 70); letter-spacing: 0.544px;\">才能完美跑出千兆网络的速度。</span></span></span></p></section></section>', 1, 0, 10, 255, '2021-12-03 10:12:23', '2021-12-03 10:12:23', '2021-12-03 10:12:23', '2023-07-21 13:48:24', '/upload/image/20211203/61a97cec01df5.jpeg', 'null', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'PC', 'zh-CN'),
