dth: 100%; caret-color: red; text-align: left; text-indent: 56px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><span style=\"caret-color: red; text-align: left; text-indent: 56px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\">大会</span><span style=\"text-align: left; text-indent: 56px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; caret-color: red; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\">以<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\">“物联芯生，数智世界”</strong>为主题，汇聚物联网、安防、智能家居等上下游产业精英，旨在打造产业前沿交流平台，加快推动行业高质量发展，促进变革时代企业的数智化转型。</span></span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: inherit; text-indent: 0em; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.75em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: inherit; text-indent: 0em; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.75em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20211209/1639033833292478.png\" title=\"1639033833292478.png\" alt=\"微信图片_20211209110445.png\"/></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: inherit; text-indent: 0em; lette