(236, 27, '五新战略开启新征程！秋叶原集团“2021年度总结表彰暨2022年度经营规划大会”胜利召开', '助人为乐、博爱奉献”--- 秋叶原爱心基金正式成立！', '<section data-role=\"outer\" label=\"Powered by 135editor.com\"><section data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"108441\" class=\"_135editor\"><section style=\"text-align: justify; margin: 10px auto;\"><p style=\"text-align:center;vertical-align:inherit;\"><strong data-brushtype=\"text\">总结表彰 展望未来</strong></p><p style=\"vertical-align:inherit;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;vertical-align: inherit;\">征程万里风正劲，继往开来逐梦行。1月18日，为全面总结2021年工作情况，表彰年度先进集体和个人，明确2022年的工作重点与工作目标，广东前海秋叶原集团<strong style=\"caret-color: red; outline-style: initial; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-indent: 34px; background-color: rgb(250, 231, 231); color: rgb(123, 12, 0); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">“2021年度总结表彰暨2022年度经营规划大会”</strong>在集团公司下属惠州产业园区胜利召开。</p><p style=\"vertical-align:inherit;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20220120/1642646411460174.jpg\" title=\"1642646411460174.jpg\" alt=\"1.webp.jpg\"/></p><p><br/></p><p>广东前海秋叶原集团董事长孙逸楷先生与集团公司、下属控股公司副经理以上管理人员及受表彰对象参加了本次会议。</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;vertical-align: inherit;\"><br/></p></section></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\" style=\"height: 0px; overflow: hidden;\"></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\"><section data-role=\"paragraph\" style=\"white-space: normal;\"><section style=\"vertical-align: inherit;line-height: 1.5em;text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20220120/1642646395547136.jpg\" title=\"1642646395547136.jpg\" alt=\"2.webp.jpg\"/></section></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\" style=\"white-space: normal;\"><section style=\"text-align: center;vertical-align: inherit;letter-spacing: 1.5px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 1px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;text-align: justify;color: #FF0000;\">广东前海秋叶原集团董事长孙逸楷先生发表重要讲话</span></strong></section></section><section style=\"vertical-align: inherit;line-height: 1.5em;\"><br/></section></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\"><section style=\"text-align: justify;vertical-align: inherit;line-height: 1.5em;\" class=\"\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span style=\"max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 1px; text-indent: 34px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; outline: none 0px !important;\">2021年，秋叶原<span style=\"max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; caret-color: red; text-indent: 12px; outline: none 0px !important;\">在董事会的英明领导下、在全体同仁及合作伙伴的共同努力</span><span style=\"max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; caret-color: red; text-indent: 37px; outline: none 0px !important;\">下，</span></span><span style=\"max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; letter-spacing: 1.5px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; outline: none 0px !important;\">克服艰难险阻<span style=\"max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; letter-spacing: 1px; text-indent: 34px;\">，</span>全面完成了年度经营规划各项任务，在“塑造秋叶原百年品牌”的大道上建立了又一光辉的里程碑！</span><span style=\"max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 1px; text-indent: 34px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; outline: none 0px !important;\">2022，我们壮志在胸、继续携手并肩、奋勇前行，激荡新时代，阔步新征程。</span></span></section></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\"><section style=\"vertical-align: inherit;line-height: 1.5em;\"><br/></section></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\"><section data-role=\"paragraph\" style=\"white-space: normal;\"><section style=\"vertical-align: inherit;line-height: 1.5em;text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20220120/1642646387451238.jpg\" title=\"1642646387451238.jpg\" alt=\"3.webp.jpg\"/></section></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\" style=\"white-space: normal;\"><p style=\"text-align:center;vertical-align: inherit;letter-spacing: 1.5px;line-height: normal;\"><strong style=\"font-size: 12px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; outline: none 0px !important;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;max-inline-size: 100%;cursor: text;color: #FF0000;outline: none 0px !important;\">广东前海秋叶原集团运营总监&amp;行政人力中心总监</span></strong></p><p style=\"text-align:center;vertical-align: inherit;letter-spacing: 1.5px;line-height: normal;\"><strong style=\"font-size: 12px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; outline: none 0px !important;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;max-inline-size: 100%;cursor: text;color: #FF0000;outline: none 0px !important;\">廖军平先生主持召开大会</span></strong></p></section><section style=\"vertical-align: inherit;line-height: 1.5em;\"><br/></section></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\"><section style=\"text-align: justify;vertical-align: inherit;line-height: 1.5em;\" class=\"\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span style=\"max-inline-size: 100%; outline-style: initial; cursor: text; caret-color: red; letter-spacing: 1px; text-indent: 34px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; outline-color: initial !important; outline-width: 0px !important;\">会上，各控股公司、职能部门及各事业部</span><span style=\"max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 1px; text-indent: 34px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; outline: none 0px !important;\">负责人围绕本部门职责和年初确定的工作目标，回顾总结了2021年工作成绩，<span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;\">剖析了存在的问题和不足，提出了具体的改进措施，并</span>对2022的工作进行了新的展望和部署。<span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;\">报告层次分明，措施改进有力，目标制定清晰。</span></span></span></section><section style=\"text-align: justify;vertical-align: inherit;line-height: 1.5em;\"><br/></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\"><section style=\"vertical-align: inherit;line-height: 1.5em;text-align: center;\" class=\"\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20220120/1642646380535582.jpg\" title=\"1642646380535582.jpg\" alt=\"4.webp.jpg\"/></section></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\"><section style=\"text-indent: 0em; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif; outline: none 0px !important;\"><p style=\"vertical-align: inherit;line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 1px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><strong style=\"max-inline-size: 100%;cursor: text;outline: none 0px !important;\"><span style=\"max-inline-size: 100%;cursor: text;text-align: justify;text-indent: 24px;color: #FF0000;outline: none 0px !important;\">广东前海秋叶原集团董事长孙逸楷先生</span></strong></span></p></section><section style=\"text-indent: 0em; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif; outline: none 0px !important;\"><p style=\"vertical-align: inherit;line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 1px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><strong style=\"max-inline-size: 100%;cursor: text;outline: none 0px !important;\"><span style=\"max-inline-size: 100%;cursor: text;text-align: justify;text-indent: 24px;color: #FF0000;outline: none 0px !important;\">听取各中心工作汇报</span></strong></span></p></section><section style=\"vertical-align: inherit;line-height: 1.5em;\"><br/></section></section></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\" class=\"\"><section style=\"text-align: justify;vertical-align: inherit;letter-spacing: 1.5px;text-indent: 0em;line-height: 1.5em;\" class=\"\"><span style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">各中心工作汇报完毕后，广东前海秋叶原集团董事长孙逸楷先生发表重要讲话。他表示：</span><span style=\"text-indent: 40px; caret-color: red; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">2021年，全球经济环境错综复杂，世界格局风云变幻。例如：贸易对抗-疫情频发-房地产严控等等。值得欣慰的是，面对如此种种不利因素，集团适时调整经营策略，各位同仁齐心协力、众志成城，总体完成了预定的规划目标。</span></section><section style=\"text-align: justify;vertical-align: inherit;letter-spacing: 1.5px;text-indent: 0em;line-height: 1.5em;\" class=\"\"><p style=\"vertical-align: inherit; text-indent: 40px; caret-color: red; font-size: 14px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><br/></p></section><p style=\"text-align:center;vertical-align:inherit;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20220120/1642646373154777.jpg\" title=\"1642646373154777.jpg\" alt=\"5.webp.jpg\"/></p><section style=\"text-align: center; max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; text-indent: 0em; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); vertical-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; outline: none 0px !important;\"><span style=\"max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; font-size: 14px; outline: none 0px !important; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><strong style=\"max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; font-size: 12px; outline: none 0px !important; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"max-inline-size: 100%;cursor: text;color: #ff0000;outline: none 0px !important;\">各中心、分子公司领导作工作汇报</span></strong></span><span style=\"text-indent: 0em;\"></span></section><section style=\"text-align: justify;vertical-align: inherit;letter-spacing: 1.5px;text-indent: 0em;line-height: 1.5em;\"><br/></section><section style=\"text-align: justify;vertical-align: inherit;letter-spacing: 1.5px;text-indent: 0em;line-height: 1.5em;\" class=\"\"><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">2021年，“秋叶原”获得了深圳500强企业榜单第96位，广东制造业企业500强第290位，第三届“安防工匠人物”、第四届“智慧安防优秀解决方案”奖，中国物联网产业品牌盛会“十大音视频品牌”榜、广东省电线电缆行业协会企业标准“领跑者”证书等嘉奖和荣誉，对各位同仁的辛勤付出和巨大努力表示衷心的感谢！</span></section><section style=\"text-align: justify;vertical-align: inherit;letter-spacing: 1.5px;text-indent: 0em;line-height: 1.5em;\"><br/></section><section style=\"text-indent: 0em; white-space: normal; max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); vertical-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.5em; text-align: center; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; outline: none 0px !important;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20220120/1642646366129171.jpg\" title=\"1642646366129171.jpg\" alt=\"6.webp.jpg\"/></section><section style=\"text-indent: 0em; white-space: normal; text-align: center; max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); vertical-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; outline: none 0px !important;\"><strong style=\"max-inline-size: 100%; outline: 0px; cursor: text; letter-spacing: 1px; font-size: 13px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"max-inline-size: 100%;outline: 0px;cursor: text;font-size: 12px;color: #ff0000;\">与会人员认真听取报告</span></strong></section><section style=\"text-align: justify;vertical-align: inherit;letter-spacing: 1.5px;text-indent: 0em;line-height: 1.5em;\"><br/></section><section style=\"text-align: justify;vertical-align: inherit;letter-spacing: 1.5px;text-indent: 0em;line-height: 1.5em;\" class=\"\"><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">数智新时代到来了，2021年10月份我们以“连接数智时代 新塑秋叶原”为主题召开的全国营销大会取得了成功，顺利拉开了数字新时代“秋叶原”品牌拓展的营销深化的序幕。<span style=\"caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">秋叶原作为一个有30多年历史的企业，要抓住数智时代的巨大机遇，</span></span><span style=\"caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); color: rgb(255, 76, 65); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><strong>以新形象、新起点、新定位、新模式、新战术，（五新战略）开启“秋叶原”发展新征程</strong></span><span style=\"caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; color: rgb(255, 76, 65); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><strong>！</strong></span></section><section style=\"text-align: justify;vertical-align: inherit;letter-spacing: 1.5px;text-indent: 0em;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; color: rgb(255, 76, 65); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><strong><br/></strong></span></section><section style=\"text-indent: 0em; white-space: normal; text-align: center; max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); vertical-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; outline: none 0px !important;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20220120/1642646359397305.jpg\" title=\"1642646359397305.jpg\" alt=\"7.webp.jpg\"/></section><section style=\"text-indent: 0em; white-space: normal; text-align: center; max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); vertical-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; outline: none 0px !important;\"><strong style=\"max-inline-size: 100%;cursor: text;outline: none 0px !important;\"><span style=\"max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-size: 12px; outline: none 0px !important; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">与会人员认真听取报告</span></strong></section><section style=\"text-align: center; max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; text-indent: 0em; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); vertical-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; outline: none 0px !important;\"><span style=\"max-inline-size: 100%;cursor: text;font-size: 12px;outline: none 0px !important;\"><strong style=\"max-inline-size: 100%;cursor: text;outline: none 0px !important;\"><span style=\"max-inline-size: 100%;cursor: text;color: #ff0000;outline: none 0px !important;\"></span></strong></span></section><section style=\"text-align: justify;vertical-align: inherit;letter-spacing: 1.5px;text-indent: 0em;line-height: 1.5em;\" class=\"\"><br/></section><section style=\"text-align: justify;vertical-align: inherit;letter-spacin